4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for individuals with no prior knowledge, aiming to become cybersecurity specialists in just 16 weeks. The program covers essential topics such as Windows and Linux administration, cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence analysis. Students participate in three live online classes per week, with class sizes capped at 16 participants. An official completion certificate is provided upon finishing the course, which is recognized by various institutions. The course materials are available in both English and Spanish. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop